        {
          "id": "4cafd0a91414_2",
          "href": null,
          "name": "8ccd",
          "text": "Our home planet is changing quickly now. Humans are a major driver of this change. We have dispersed from equatorial environments to fill many social niches — altering landscapes and the composition of life as we went.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4cafd0a91414_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "49ca",
          "text": "Now we are in the midst of planetary-scale collapse that is of our own making. Life continues to evolve with conditions for mass extinction and dramatic disruptions to Earth’s climate system. Millions of people have experienced displacements due to intensified hurricanes, expanding deserts (and the conflicts they cause), and virulent wildfires.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 51,
              "href": "https://anchor.fm/emerge/episodes/Joe-Brewer---State-of-the-Collapse-e2av6i",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 27,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4cafd0a91414_4",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4e34",
          "text": "Yet almost no one is talking about this as an evolutionary process.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4cafd0a91414_5",
          "href": null,
          "name": "ed32",
          "text": "We can apply the tools used to study cultural evolution to build resilience in our communities and weather the storms of the coming century. In order to do this we will need to integrate the biological and social sciences and take a holistic approach to the management of our institutions.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
