        {
          "id": "4cafd0a91414_6",
          "href": null,
          "name": "ab13",
          "text": "I have written extensively about the need for a global network of culture design labs to do this work. My colleagues and I are building momentum to kick off 2019 in a big way. We are setting out to regenerate an entire bioregion in Costa Rica — where we are establishing a School for Applied Cultural Evolution as the intellectual center for learning how to guide the evolution of the entire Earth System.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
